snippet.title: Micro Machines (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Micro Machines (PS2) - Driver: Danger Ranger - Cup: Bronze

Micro Machines is a fast action game with a wide selection of tracks in a number of different environments. Players select one out of many vehicles and one out of eight characters. Each of the different characters will have different abilities and personality.
